text: Aleksandar Bakić (born 3 September 2000) is a Montenegrin handball player for RK Komovi and the Montenegrin national team.Player profile He represented Montenegro at the 2020 European Men's Handball Championship.2020 European Men's Handball Championship squad ==References== ==External links== * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Montenegrin male handball players Category:People from Berane
